        "main_heading": "Naturally Better: The Benefits of Our Wool",
        "heading_size": "h2",
        "sub_heading": "Why Choose Wool",
        "main_text": "<p>The wool that is taken off of our lambs is around the 29 micron mark, which tells us that it's well suited to products such as clothing like jerseys, socks and scarves, as well as insulation and carpet. <br/><br/>Wool is a product with a large number of benefits, health and otherwise. It's a natural solution when insulating the house and carpeting the home, it's a breathable fibre and perfect for keeping you warm in the colder months. <br/><br/>It's also a New Zealand produced alternative to many imported synthetic products.<br/><br/>Learn more about the benefits of wool <a href=\"https://woolsnz.co.nz/wool-supply/\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p>",
